week1
Week 1 quick start guide for running TalentLens-AI.

1) Create and activate a Python virtual environment.
   - python -m venv .venv
   - source .venv/bin/activate
2) Install project dependencies.
   - pip install -r requirements.txt
3) Configure Kaggle access.
   - export KAGGLE_USERNAME=your_username
   - export KAGGLE_KEY=your_key
   - or place kaggle.json in ~/.kaggle/
   - update data/kaggle_datasets.json with correct dataset slugs
4) Download and normalize datasets.
   - python -m talentlens.data.kaggle
   - python -m talentlens.data.normalize
   - python -m talentlens.data.policies
5) Build the resume-only index.
   - python -m talentlens.rag.index
6) Run the API server.
   - uvicorn main:app --reload
